   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Make the following checks semi-annually:</p>
            <ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Perform the <xref href="Bruce_Monthly_Check_CPT_DD00515393.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Read out the event log and analyze it. If any irregularities
are found that cannot be explained, please contact your local <xref conref="../../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Visual inspection of the system (without turning off the system).</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Only for systems with filter mats:</b> Check if the filter
mats are dirty. It is important to replace the filter mats when needed
to ensure sufficient cooling. If the filter mats are dirty replace
them. See the section <xref href="#./CheckAndReplaceTheFilterMats-B10D3A6B"
                           scope="local"
                           type="section"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>. </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Based on the findings during this check make necessary preparations
for the annual maintenance.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section id="CheckAndReplaceTheFilterMats-B10D3A6B" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Check and
replace the filter mats</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <table frame="none" class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="150.00px" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry colsep="0" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <image href="../../Images/MM_PxW-WxW-SDC_Remove-filter-mat_0000327529.svg"
                                  placement="inline"
                                  class="- topic/image "/>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="bottom" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                              <sli class="- topic/sli ">
                                 <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> Ventilation grid</sli>
                              <sli class="- topic/sli ">
                                 <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> Filter mat</sli>
                           </sl>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
            <ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screws on the ventilation grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the ventilation grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the filter mat <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> by sliding it out from under
the system.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Check if the filter mat <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> is dirty or needs to be
replaced straight away.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Insert a new filter mat <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> or the cleaned old filter
mat <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Attach the ventilation grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Fasten the screws in the ventilation grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
